Yimɓe ɓe ɗo mari kuugal waɗugo ɗo - ko yotti biliyon 1.5 hande, biliyon 2.5 yahugo 2030 - kamɓe on ɓuri kala nukkure yimɓe fuu mawnugo bee law haa nder duuniyaaru.
