Ley wakkati on, gofernama leydi Mexique filake waartirii El Casillo ( ɓaade Kukulcan) e faa hannden nokku annditirteeɗo Grand Cour de Bal.
Thompson, tawaakanonaa leydi Amirki kaa ruuɗaaki Yucatan gatin.
